<h2 style="margin: 10px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; color: #646464; line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: #fafafa;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; background-color: #ffffff;">Here are our Terms and Conditions for customer bookings, re-scheduling or missed appointments.</span></h2>
<p style="background-position: 0px 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; vertical-align: baseline;"> </p>
<p style="background-position: 0px 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="background-position: 0px 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline;" class="font_6">Our Service</span><span style="background-position: 0px 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline;" class="font_6">..</span></p>
